        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6913",
        "content": "At the door, now closed, Jane gave a single knock; they were admitted by Clem, who, in regarding Kirkwood, wore her haughtiest demeanour.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
