        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6913",
        "content": "A few meaningless pictures hung here and there, and on the mantel piece, which sloped forward somewhat, stood some paltry ornaments, secured in their places by a piece of string stretched in front of them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
